Hi Thiago,

I think you want a hierarchical model.

bird_richness ~ Poisson(mu_br)
log(mu_br) = Season + Pool

zooplankton ~ Poisson(mu_zp)
log(mu_zp) = Season + Pool + mu_br

I think that is is feasible to fit such model with the INLA package (
www.r-inla.org).

